==================== TEXT & LOG COMMANDS ====================

-------------------- VIEW FILE --------------------
tac linux.txt           →       show file in reverse (last line first)
rev linux.txt           →       reverse each line content
wc linux.txt            →       count lines, words, characters

-------------------- HEAD (TOP LINES) --------------------
head                    →       show first 10 lines (default)
head -n 20 app.log      →       show first 20 lines
head -n 25 app.log      →       show first 25 lines

-------------------- TAIL (BOTTOM LINES) --------------------
tail                    →       show last 10 lines (default)
tail app.log            →       show last 10 lines of file
tail -n 20 app.log      →       show last 20 lines

-------------------- SEARCH (GREP) --------------------
grep                    →       search text in file
grep 'apache' app.log   →       search 'apache'
grep -i 'java' app.log  →       case-insensitive search
grep -i 'exception' app.log →   search 'exception' (ignore case)
grep -n 'exception' app.log →   show line numbers
grep -v 'apache' app.log →      exclude 'apache' lines

