==================== VI EDITOR CHEAT SHEET ====================

-------------------- MODES --------------------
Normal Mode        →       default mode (for navigation & commands)
Insert Mode        →       for typing/editing text
Command Mode       →       for save, quit, search (uses :)

-------------------- SWITCH MODES --------------------
i                  →       insert before cursor
a                  →       insert after cursor
o                  →       new line below
O                  →       new line above
Esc                →       back to Normal mode

-------------------- SAVE & EXIT --------------------
:w                 →       save file
:q                 →       quit
:wq                →       save and quit
:x                 →       save and quit
:q!                →       quit without saving

-------------------- NAVIGATION --------------------
h                  →       move left
l                  →       move right
k                  →       move up
j                  →       move down
0                  →       move to line start
$                  →       move to line end
gg                 →       go to first line
G                  →       go to last line
:n                 →       go to line number n

-------------------- EDITING --------------------
x                  →       delete character
dd                 →       delete full line
yy                 →       copy (yank) line
p                  →       paste below
P                  →       paste above
u                  →       undo
Ctrl + r           →       redo

-------------------- SEARCH --------------------
/text              →       search forward
?text              →       search backward
n                  →       next match
N                  →       previous match

-------------------- VISUAL MODE --------------------
v                  →       select text
V                  →       select full line
y                  →       copy selected
d                  →       delete selected

